<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5043471>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–8. Makalapobius aigrettensis n. gen. n. sp. 1, Male paratype in dorsal view (specimen 2011MauRod026). 2, same in side view. 3, same, face. 4, same, left hind leg in outer view. 5, same in inner view. 6, same, SGP, flattened. 7, same, right FW, flattened. 8, female paratype (specimen 2011MauRod027): Ovp in left side view (top) and in ventral view (bottom). Scales: 1–2: 10 mm; 3–8: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5043471/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5043473>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–11. Makalapobius aigrettensis n. gen. n. sp. stridulation in natura (specimen BIOTAS2008 424, afternoon, 30°C; in a cave). 11, power spectrum of 10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5043473/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5043475>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–18. Makalapobius masihu n. gen. n. sp. 12, Male holotype in dorsal view. 13, same, face. 14, same, left FIII in outer view. 15, same, SGP, not flattened. 16, same, FW. 17–18, female allotype. 17, Ovp in right side view. 18, body in right side view. Scales: 12: 5 mm; 13–18: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5043475/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5043477>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19–24. Makalapobius n. gen. male genitalia. 19–21, Makalapobius aigrettensis n. gen. n. sp.; Makalapobius masihu n. gen. n. sp. Left panels: dorsal views; middle panel: ventral views; right panels: left side views. Scale: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5043477/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5043493>
    dc:description "FIGURES 71–76. Makalapobius n. gen. (71–72) and Gabusibius n. gen. (73–76) in natura. 71–72, Makalapobius aigrettensis n. gen. n. sp. 73–74, Gabusibius mosi n. gen. n. sp. 75–76, Gabusibius dzindzanu n. gen. n. sp. Left panels are males, right panels are females." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5043493/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5043495>
    dc:description "FIGURE 77. Distribution of Makalapobius n. gen. and Gabusibius n. gen. in South Western Indian Ocean." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5043495/files/figure.png" ;
